    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-04-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-04-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="266"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d266">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Campbell</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Orleans,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-04-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 6, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your despatch by telegraph received. Presuming that the department expects me to
                    make the communication to President Juarez by special bearer of <pb facs="0459"
                        n="389" xml:id="pg_389"/> despatches, I will forthwith adopt measures to
                    send one to Queretaro via Tampico, unless otherwise instructed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LEWIS D. CAMPBELL.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
